{
  "stem": "3928.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to go to the island of Chapel Island when I met the partisans, you know, at a certain place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are taking over the people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the following day, I got the message that's my father and my brother was killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To find out about them, and they shot them right there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So that's the tragedy of life, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You say, you-- you know, you do what you think is right to do, you know, and you can save your own family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's stuck with me for a long time, you know, but I just was out of my control what I could do, you know, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had to live with it for a long time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, I'm still living with this, you know, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I couldn't do nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They did not want to leave because still had certain things to do there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I could have taken with me right there and then, because I-- I not even used headquarters car for this, you know, because I-- I-- you know, if people would have find out, you know, they would get it all around the car, you know, a German military car, you know, and then somebody would recognize me.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As a civilian, I could go if without anybody really paying to-- any attention to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I used the train back and forth, which was a short ride, train ride, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unfortunately, next day-- my aunt actually told me this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I told them I have to go to get my father, and my aunt told me, he said, it's-- you don't have to go.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
